{"tid":671869,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"敗陣餘波？摩連奴刪IG戶口","createTime":"2018-05-20T13:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T00:57:20.000Z","uid":16659,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ee906e8a37f675db13045246a295ba1c0bccb05e","tid":671869,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T13:16:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/9/359/21502933359/21502451395_600x389.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F9%2F359%2F21502933359%2F21502451395_600x389.jpg&h=a32f68eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=iuB4Kbp2SxvtDCaeU8NJMuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=0c111ff6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯今季最後一個錦標落空，主帥摩連奴似乎在網上受到猛烈抨擊，最終選擇「斬腳趾避沙蟲」。<br />\n<br />\n摩連奴（Jose Mourinho）性格「唔輸得」人所共知，在今次網絡事件當中可見一斑。在曼聯不敵車路士，失去今季英格蘭足總盃後，憤怒的球迷按捺不住，在摩連奴社交網站中批評紅魔表現，甚至質疑摩連奴的點兵佈陣。<br />\n<br />\n面對排山倒海負評，摩連奴看來選擇一個最簡單的解決方法，直接刪除戶口，現時在網上搜尋亦無法找到他的Instagram。據稱摩連奴的戶口擁有280萬追隨者，有網民表示今次事件是「網絡欺凌」，令摩連奴的忠心支持者受到傷害。<br />\n<br />\n今季摩連奴帶領的曼聯成績未算出色，以次席完成英超聯賽算是比較亮眼，但歐聯、足總盃、聯賽盃俱鎩羽而歸，以四大皆空的尷尬姿態完成賽季。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"d85326ccaa64d4218adb081f099bf1be50d58c83","tid":671869,"uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T13:16:42.000Z","msg":"摩二季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4041e2ba85ce88a7ea68fb6a225e8843752e1f","tid":671869,"uid":7854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T13:17:58.000Z","msg":"廢閪 搞到輸錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c4355504e4b55690e02d95a9f6b81738d43745","tid":671869,"uid":41107,"like":